title: Denmark Heads for Period of Uncertainty After Snap Election
description: With no clear coalition as of Tuesday night, the stage is set for a negotiation to form what analysts say will likely be a centrist government.
dc:creator: Jasmina Nielsen and Isabella Kwai
media:description: Campaign posters in Copenhagen last month. In a crowded field of more than a dozen parties — including some newcomers — analysts said that the election could throw up some surprises.
